## Supabase Tables

| Table | Purpose |
|---|---|
| `products` | Product master (code, name, uom, rate, cgst, sgst, igst, discount) |
| `ledgers` | Ledger/party master (name, group, opening_balance) |
| `uoms` | Unit of Measure master (name) |
| `vouchers` | Sales & Purchase invoice headers |
| `voucherItems` | Line items for vouchers (FK: voucher_id, product_id) |
| `receiptPayments` | Receipt and Payment vouchers |
| `company` | Company/business profile settings |
| `users` | User management (name, email, role) |

