## 📋 FULL TESTING TASK LIST (After Fixing the 404)

The user wants **1 random entry tested on every page**. Here's the test plan:

### 1. UOM Master (`/uom`)
- Add a UOM: `LTR`
- Verify it appears in the table

### 2. Product Master (`/products`)
- Add product: Code=`1234`, Name=`Test Oil`, UOM=`LTR`, Rate=`500`, CGST=`9`, SGST=`9`, IGST=`0`, Disc=`0`
- Verify it appears in the table

### 3. Ledger Master (`/ledgers`)
- Add ledger: Name=`Test Customer`, Group=`Sundry Debtors`, Opening Balance=`0`
- Verify it appears

### 4. Sales Invoice (`/sales`)
- Select Party: `Test Customer`
- Add row: select `Test Oil`, Qty=`2`
- Save invoice → confirm ID shown in alert
- Verify in History

### 5. Purchase Invoice (`/purchase`)
- Add a purchase entry with `Test Oil`, Qty=`5`
- Save → confirm ID

### 6. Receipt & Payment (`/receipt-payment`)
- Record Receipt: Ledger=`Test Customer`, Amount=`1000`, Remarks=`Test Receipt`
- Verify entry in table

### 7. Invoice History (`/history`)
- Filter by Sales → verify the sales invoice is there
- Filter by Purchase → verify the purchase invoice

### 8. Home Dashboard (`/`)
- Check KPI cards update (Total Revenue, Amount Received, Outstanding Dues, Clients)
- Click Sync Data button

### 9. Settings (`/settings`)
- Save company profile: Name=`My Test Business`, GST=`29ABCDE1234F1Z5`
- Add a user: Name=`Admin User`, Email=`admin@test.com`, Role=`Admin`
- Delete the test user

