## Key Source Files Summary

### `src/db/supabaseClient.js`
```js
import { createClient } from '@supabase/supabase-js';
const supabaseUrl = 'https://jskpwjbffldjsnawjcsp.supabase.co';
const supabaseKey = 'sb_publishable_7BHFB14bhgBYQIxmzc7B8g_72c9aWrX';
export const supabase = createClient(supabaseUrl, supabaseKey);
```

### `src/hooks/useSupabaseCollection.js`
- Custom hook: fetches data from any Supabase table and subscribes to real-time changes
- Returns array of records sorted by `id` ascending
- Real-time: handles INSERT, UPDATE, DELETE events

### `src/App.jsx`
- Uses `BrowserRouter` + React Router v6
- Nav links: Home, Sales, Purchase, Receipt/Pymt, History | Products, Ledgers, UOM, Settings
- Online/Offline indicator (green/red dot) next to brand name

