> [!IMPORTANT]
> After the new agent session starts, the very first step should be:
> 1. Create `vercel.json` at project root
> 2. Run `push.bat` (or `git add . && git commit -m "fix vercel SPA routing" && git push`)
> 3. Wait for Vercel to redeploy (~1-2 min)
> 4. Test all pages as listed above

